C++Blueprint <pre><code>void UInvitationWidget::ShowInvitation(const FFWGuildInvitation&amp; Invitation)
{
    GuildNameText-&gt;SetText(FText::FromString(Invitation.GuildName));
    InviterText-&gt;SetText(FText::FromString(
        FString::Printf(TEXT("Invited by %s"),
            *Invitation.InvitedByDisplayName)));

    // Calculate time remaining
    FTimespan Remaining = Invitation.ExpiresAt - FDateTime::UtcNow();
    ExpiryText-&gt;SetText(FText::FromString(
        FString::Printf(TEXT("Expires in %d hours"),
            FMath::Max(0, (int32)Remaining.GetTotalHours()))));

    CachedInvitationId = Invitation.InvitationId;
    SetVisibility(ESlateVisibility::Visible);
}
</code></pre> <ol> <li>Create a widget with text fields for guild name, inviter name, and expiry time.</li> <li>Add Accept and Decline buttons.</li> <li>On the On Invitation Received event, call <code>ShowInvitation</code> with the invitation data.</li> <li>Wire Accept to a custom "Accept Invitation" function on the player controller.</li> <li>Wire Decline to a custom "Decline Invitation" function.</li> </ol>

